entry.title: Santa's Magic Front Door Key
entry.summary:
Vendor: Wholesale Princess
Type: Home - Decorations

If your home or the home of someone you know does not have a chimney for "Santa" lots of times little ones wonder how he is going to get in. Our Adorable "Santa's Magic Key" is a great little way to let them know that it is no problem for the Jolly Man to get in with this Magic Key.
Our Key comes attached to card stock with a little verse for you to share with your little ones. Hopefully you can use the verse to get them to go to sleep LOL.

The card stock is cut to easily hang on your door.


To Leave your gifts beneath the tree, I'm giving you this magic key.

Before you sleep you'll have a chore, please hang this key outside your door.

Then go to bed, turn off your light, and Santa Clause will come tonight!
